metadata.name: in a symphony
metadata.description:
From the ocean's cradle, I emerge anew,
Stepping on earthly shores, adorned in dew.
Beneath the sun's warm touch, my spirit soars,
Embracing its radiance, my heart restores.

Whispering zephyrs guide my tranquil quest,
Revealing nature's secrets, in stillness blessed.
Like waves in a symphony, I dance with grace,
Creating ripples of peace in this hallowed space.

The sea's embrace imparts serene repose,
Symbolic of rebirth, where solace flows.
I merge with the world, in harmony's embrace,
A tranquil soul, content with life's embrace.

Seray & ai
